                      <td valign="top" height="100%"><font face="arial" size="2" color="#000000"><span class="spnMessageText" id="msg"> To be honest, I do not think that HP&gt;mana applies until you get to at least 45-50. Before, you need all the mana you can get to solo the biggest mobs possible and level. After those levels, mana becomes less an issue and HPs will limit your soloing ability. The rule of thumb I was given, and which I stil think applies to blues server, is get your int to 200. Then worry about HPs. When you get to 2k hps unbuffed, start working on focus and mana.</span id="msg"></font><br><br></td>
