                      <td colspan="2" valign="top">
                      <font color="#000000" face="arial" size="2">Posted&nbsp;-&nbsp;10/03/2003&nbsp;:&nbsp; 10:31:49 AM</font>
                      &nbsp;<a href="pop_profile.asp?mode=display&id=1900"><img src="images/icon_profile.gif" width="15" height="15" border="0" alt="Show Profile" title="Show Profile" align="absmiddle" hspace="6" /></a>
                      &nbsp;<a href="post.asp?method=ReplyQuote&REPLY_ID=222104&TOPIC_ID=22931&FORUM_ID=13"><img src="images/icon_reply_topic.gif" width="15" height="15" border="0" alt="Reply with Quote" title="Reply with Quote" align="absmiddle" hspace="6" /></a>
                      <hr noshade size="2"></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td valign="top" height="100%"><font face="arial" size="2" color="#000000"><span class="spnMessageText" id="msg"> A not so simple calculation is level/5 * int = mana. So, at level 20, each int = 4m. at level 30 each int = 6m. This is up to 200 int. Past 200 int, 1 int = 6 mana.<br /><br />So getting to 200 int shouldn't really be your target. Having more mana is more important than having a higher intelligence.<br /><br />As for Zerp's suggestion that you get 200 int, then get HP, get 2khp then get foci, (for bluebies) I disagree. The most important foci should be gotten first. mana pres (for groupers where you nuke lots), and Aff-efficiency should be gotten by kiters. Saving 10-25% of your mana costs will FAR outweigh having a larger mana pool. If you're mana pool's 800 mana (reasonable at L20), you can cast 11 siphon lifes, with mp, you can cast 12. You'd have to add another 64 mana (hard to do that young) to tap 12 times w/o MP. <br /><br />Same situation: 800m, L20, infetious cloud (78m), 10 casts w/o aff-eff. with aff-eff, 13 casts. 3 more casts would take 200 more mana w/o aff-eff. <br /><br />Get affliction efficiency and mana preservation. They're the BEST use of your money upgrading over anything else.</span id="msg"></font><br><br></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td valign="bottom"><font color="#000000" face="arial" size="2"><span class="spnMessageText"> <img src="http://members.aol.com/myinternetpix/EQ/avatars/A_Badger_Porn_Avatar_01.gif" border="0"> Sage <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=799061" target="_blank">[Ahkwell Foley]</a> Loot Lichzard</span></font></td>
